Comprehensive platform designed to support school, college, and university students.

# For Students and IT Graduates
- Specialized focus on post-syllabus topics with concise explanations and one-on-one courses.
- Academic project support: Offering AI-based academic projects with end-to-end hosting services.
- Recorded and live sessions: Providing machine learning recorded content and live group sessions.
- Professional transition classes: Intensive training for graduates to become industry-ready, covering Git, Linux, Frontend, Backend, and Networking basics.
- Educational video library: Links to YouTube content to drive engagement and student enrollment.
- Career guidance: Providing strategic advice for students entering the IT field.
- Remote learning: All sessions are conducted via Zoom or other delivery platforms rather than on the website itself.
- Focused purpose: The website serves as a gateway to enroll students in classes; it does not include internal testing, valuations, or a Udemy-style learning management system.

# For Professionals
- Backend and System Design fundamentals.
- Containerization and Monitoring: Docker, Docker Compose, and observability stacks (ELK, Prometheus, Grafana).
- Advanced Golang: In-depth concepts including Goroutines, concurrency, and performance optimization.
- Live Infrastructure Hosting: Deploying projects to VPS with custom domain integration.
- End-to-end Deployment: Covering domain registration, server management, reverse proxies, and application hosting.
- Serverless Deployment: Hosting projects on serverless platforms like Cloudflare and Google Cloud Run.
- AI and RAG-based Projects: Hands-on implementation of Retrieval-Augmented Generation.
- Modern AI Tech Stack: Leveraging Ollama, ChromaDB, Vector Databases, and Semantic Search.